.TH smi-software "1" "October 2025" "SMI Toolset 0.100.0" "SMI Base Command"
.SH NAME
smi-software \- Print the SMI software configuration path (Deprecated)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B smi-software
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
.B smi-software
